Package com.ebay.sdk

Interface Summary
EBayConstants  
ErrorInfo Interface to identify that a data object can store related error.
SendApiRequestListener Listner for sending API SOAP request event.
TokenEventListener Listener to handle token events such as soft-expiration-renew and hard-expiration-warning.
 

Class Summary
ApiAccount Defines an eBay API account object.
ApiCall The base class of all API call classes (AddItemCall, GetItemCall, etc).
ApiContext Defines the API context with which an API call will be made.
ApiCredential Defines credentials to be used for making eBay API call.
ApiLogging Contains properties to control SDK logging.
ApiSchemaBasedXmlPoster Making Schema-based API (non-SOAP) call by posting Schema-based Xml request string to the traditional eBay API server.
CallRetry Defines failure-retry condition for API call.
eBayAccount Defines eBay auction account.
ErrorInfoImpl Implementation of ErrorAware interface.
ExceptionFilter Implements exception matching for call retry and for exception payload logging.
SiteIDUtil Utility class the converts between SiteCodeType and eBay numerical Site ID.
TimeFilter Title:
 

Exception Summary
ApiException Represents one or more errors reported by an API call.
SdkException The super class of all SDK exception types.
SdkHTTPException Wraps HTTP exception (unexpected return codes 300 - 499, 501-599) for SDK.
SdkSoapException Wraps SOAP exception (SOAPFaultException) for SDK.
